# Codex Configuration - Angular 5→20 Migration

## Project Context
Angular 5.2.0 → Angular 20 progressive migration
- Library: pwc-ui-shared-v4-ia (migrate first)
- App: pwc-ui-v4-ia (migrate second)

## Critical Constraints

### No Admin Rights
- Cannot use sudo
- Cannot install globally (npm install -g)
- Use local npm installs only

### Keep Repos Clean
- Never create test/debug files in pwc-ui-shared-v4-ia/ or pwc-ui-v4-ia/
- Use scripts_outils_ia/ for temporary files
- Delete temp files after use

### Document Everything
Update docs_outils_ia/JOURNAL-COORDINATION.md daily:
- Date and action
- Results
- Issues and solutions
- Next steps

### Test-Driven Development (TDD)
1. Write test (red)
2. Implement (green)
3. Refactor (still green)
4. Commit

## Migration Strategy

5→6→7→8 (Foundation)
→ 9→10→11→12 (Ivy)
→ 13→14→15 (Standalone)
→ 16→17 (Signals)
→ 18→19→20 (Modern)

Order: pwc-ui-shared-v4-ia THEN pwc-ui-v4-ia

## Best Practices

- SOLID principles
- Clean code
- TypeScript strict mode
- OnPush change detection
- Unsubscribe from observables
- Atomic git commits

## File Locations

✅ scripts_outils_ia/ - temporary scripts
✅ docs_outils_ia/ - documentation
❌ pwc-ui-shared-v4-ia/ - no temp files
❌ pwc-ui-v4-ia/ - no temp files

## Checklist Per Step

- [ ] Write tests (TDD)
- [ ] Update dependencies
- [ ] Run tests (pass)
- [ ] Build (success)
- [ ] Update docs
- [ ] Commit

## Safe Commands

```bash
✅ npm install <package>
✅ npm test / npm run build
✅ git add/commit/push
❌ npm install -g
❌ sudo
```

